## Conflict

* Despite everyone's best intention and good will, there is usually some small amount of disagreement or conflict. 
  * This is totally normal and to be expected. 
  * In fact when you see it happening you can think to yourself: "Aha, there it is, I was expecting this and I can roll with it."
  * But very occasionally things can suddenly become really challenging. Here are some tips:

<%= include_image "/content/topics/images/fsnp.jpg" %>

:slide_title Challenges

* Working in teams can suddenly become CHALLENGING
* There is a non-zero probability that you will not get along with someone in your team
  * Be ready for this and take it in stride. "Whoops, there it is!"
* You are not married, you are not best friends, you are just working on this project, now
* Don't try to resolve the conflict in email, it never works!
* Fight the reluctance to have to sit with someone and talk about an awkward subject.

